      ** APPLICATIONS INSTALLED
     A            ZZOE           1A         TEXT('ORDER ENTRY/BILLING')
     A                                      COLHDG('O/E')
     A            ZZAR           1A         TEXT('ACCOUNTS RECEIVABLE')
     A                                      COLHDG('A/R')
     A            ZZIC           1A         TEXT('INVENTORY')
     A                                      COLHDG('I/C')
     A            ZZSA           1A         TEXT('SALES ANALYSIS')
